{"tid":1534214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記住每個星期六都要幫機場做壓力測試","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T02:51:36.000Z","uid":274576,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a6016252e236fdbbf7b19d2218066277d762d48e","tid":1534214,"uid":274576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:42:47.000Z","msg":"不如討論下究竟點先可以揸好呢個春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次入機場都有不完美可改善嘅地方 但無可否認機場亦係最少手足被拘捕 不如集思廣益究竟之後每個星期六要點做<br />\n<br />\n個人認為機場要和理非到極致<br />\n旅客裝 欣賞下香港機場同埋研究機場交通<br />\n見到狗都唔洗理佢 因為你係冇犯法 唔好一見狗就即刻話要散水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果驚嘅就一早買定單程廉航機票（幾百蚊啫） 或者買張可以退嘅機票 帶埋passport做足準備<br />\n有咩事咪入去客運大樓囉吹你唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Ud50W3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Ud50W3.png&h=90bb3620&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6180eb6df30607a30adecb0ec57cd2db055d277c","tid":1534214,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:43:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10eb411ccbd6d0a32f63d67841fe9c868d2b52ff","tid":1534214,"uid":285855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:45:06.000Z","msg":"香港回歸未定案嫁<br />\n<br />\n借一下位, 純手動po請見諒<br />\n<br />\n侵侵叫大陸還清朝債卷<br />\n大陸唔肯還成10萬億美金<br />\n佢話前朝唔認佢要還<br />\n如果唔駛還唔認點解要還香港<br />\nbloomberg同台灣都有講, 點解香港無聲氣<br />\n還, 大陸還唔起<br />\n唔還我地仲係英殖地<br />\n如果借據美國買左我地係美殖地<br />\n就算還都應該係還俾有還錢的政府, 我地就係台灣人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.c